  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord Community</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/bbc532868943fb93f222d13871800a37.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you wish to report a bug or just chat with us, join us in discord!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/4a8503578460bd6ebbe6946d5c6fec2a.poster.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/4a8503578460bd6ebbe6946d5c6fec2a.webm?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/4a8503578460bd6ebbe6946d5c6fec2a.mp4?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every replay is different, every change or direction creates a random new set of threats around the player. Nothing is the same, and nothing is predictable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter \"Endless Mode\" to hunt the biggest high score. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And remember, do not collide with \"The World Killer\". Any collision with him is game over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/55ef1710714e05ffc054cf457c241cf0.poster.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/55ef1710714e05ffc054cf457c241cf0.webm?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/55ef1710714e05ffc054cf457c241cf0.mp4?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starting as an innocent asteroid your goal is to evolve and progress to larger stages. Collide with smaller asteroids and evolve to the planet stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/d1483b8a6ba8c1791925207ea1c1592f.poster.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/d1483b8a6ba8c1791925207ea1c1592f.webm?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/d1483b8a6ba8c1791925207ea1c1592f.mp4?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you grow and become the source of all light in the universe your journey is not over. Do not hit any larger objects until you are pulled into a black hole.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/9d312e14377b1eeca3d5b6e48da08069.poster.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/9d312e14377b1eeca3d5b6e48da08069.webm?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/9d312e14377b1eeca3d5b6e48da08069.mp4?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/4a8503578460bd6ebbe6946d5c6fec2a.poster.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/4a8503578460bd6ebbe6946d5c6fec2a.webm?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/4a8503578460bd6ebbe6946d5c6fec2a.mp4?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every replay is different, every change or direction creates a random new set of threats around the player. Nothing is the same, and nothing is predictable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter \"Endless Mode\" to hunt the biggest high score. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And remember, do not collide with \"The World Killer\". Any collision with him is game over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/55ef1710714e05ffc054cf457c241cf0.poster.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/55ef1710714e05ffc054cf457c241cf0.webm?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/55ef1710714e05ffc054cf457c241cf0.mp4?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starting as an innocent asteroid your goal is to evolve and progress to larger stages. Collide with smaller asteroids and evolve to the planet stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/d1483b8a6ba8c1791925207ea1c1592f.poster.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/d1483b8a6ba8c1791925207ea1c1592f.webm?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/d1483b8a6ba8c1791925207ea1c1592f.mp4?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you grow and become the source of all light in the universe your journey is not over. Do not hit any larger objects until you are pulled into a black hole.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/9d312e14377b1eeca3d5b6e48da08069.poster.avif?t=1728557759\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/9d312e14377b1eeca3d5b6e48da08069.webm?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540160/extras/9d312e14377b1eeca3d5b6e48da08069.mp4?t=1728557759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
